Package: procflow
Version: 1.0.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: procflow
Depends: python3, python3-bpfcc
Suggests: man-db
Description: Process-enriched network flow logger
 eBPF-based tool that captures TCP and UDP flows and enriches each record
 with host OS context: process name, PID, UID, username, and (for inbound
 TCP sessions) the authenticated PAM username of the connecting user.
 Output is newline-delimited JSON written to a rotating log file and stdout.
